text: I mean who could have predicted that (apart from Yuri and his spoons)
author: wallace_anna

text: I think we’re a long way away from David Miliband being the answer. But through the Brexit fog we do need to focus on the reforms needed - whether a change of re-emphasis or more substantive.
author: wallace_anna

text: Love Brexit or loathe it, this is one consequence of the result which we shouldn’t lose sight of. There are parts of the UK for whom the current system hasn’t worked and we should fix that.
author: wallace_anna

text: Great fun recording with you both! #Brexit
author: wallace_anna
